<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/China-to-build-agricultural-research-facility-in-Mali" title="China to build agricultural research facility in Mali " alt="link">China to build agricultural research facility in Mali </a></h2>

	
					<p>China plans to build a centre for agricultural research and technological demonstration near Bamako, Mali, to carry out experiments and technical training, and to contribute to the development of sustainable agriculture in the country, SciDev reports (7/8/2012).</p>
